At the very least you should be able to use this set of instructions
to install the module...

perl Build.PL
./Build
./Build test
./Build install

Git repo:
    git clone http://technosorcery.net/git/jifty-auth-bitcard

    http://technosorcery.net/git/?p=jifty-auth-bitcard

Mailing list:
    jifty-plugin-authen-bitcard@lists.technosorcery.net

    http://lists.technosorcery.net/listinfo.cgi/jifty-plugin-authen-bitcard-technosorcery.net

Bugs:
